'''Klasse Ephemora''' was a [[Star/Legends|star]] located in the [[Klasse Ephemora system/Legends|Klasse Ephemora system]] of the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]]. It was [[Orbit/Legends|orbited]] by the [[Gas giant/Legends|gas giant]] [[Mobus/Legends|Mobus]], its seventeen [[Moon/Legends|moons]], and the living free-floating [[Planet/Legends|planet]] named [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]].

